      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours condition. At its heart lies the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Vanos system that has been meticulously overhauled for optimal valve timing. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a Variable M Differential Lock, ensuring surgical precision during lateral transitions. The chassis has been proactively reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points to maintain structural rigidity beyond factory standards. With zero oxidation on the undercarriage and a factory-spec suspension that remains tight and communicative, this specimen offers a pure, analog driving experience that is mechanically indistinguishable from the day it left Regensburg.",
